<br>
Riding right upto the sea god, he says words that damage any relationship they had.<br>
<br>
&quot;I'm not on your side, uncle I never will be. Give up this lost cause before I do it for you&quot;<br>
<br>
The black eyes of the dark prince of Olympus gleamed with the excitement of war.<br>
<br>
&quot;I will never forgive you for attacking the amazons...NEVER!...you forget that they are family to me! Now you pay the price!&quot;<br>
<br>
With that he flipped off his horse and stood in front of Poseidon. Lifting the sword of war into a fighting position. He felt the energy and power from the sword that he felt every time he was about to fight.<br>
<br>
He went to attack the sea god.<br>
<br>
&quot;You can't win this war... I am war, uncle!&quot;<br>
<br>
and with a cry he lunged his sword... <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#6A74B4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uamazondelerium.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Amazon DeLerium</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Amazon</span><br>  Posts: 179<br> <font color=#FFFF00>(11/22/01 7:17 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm32.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=7.topic&index=170>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://members.aol.com/deleriuml9/images/del2.bmp WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Charges</span><hr size=1> ~ She looked over to Varia for the mment she had before charging back into the battle.~<br>
