<br>
Her gaze locked on Hypnos and her eyes turned red with rage. <p><html> <font face="Signet Roundhand ATT"> Varia Angelina Avande </font> </html></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#6A74B4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/unikeqofv.showPublicProfile?language=EN>NikeQofV</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Bronze Warrior</span><br>  Posts: 112<br> <font color=#FFFF00>(11/23/01 9:18 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm32.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=7.topic&index=176>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.btinternet.com/~dave.newton/lysette-anthony/pictures/lysette-anthony109.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Decision</span><hr size=1> ::a golden shimmery rainbow glows in on place. In the rainbow appears Nike. The rainbow slowly fades away. A few steps away, a small marble staircase appears with an ivory and gold throne upon it. Slowly and gracefully, Nike ascends the staircase in a princess like white shimmery gown with two pearl bracelets with her curly, rich, fiery red hair pinned up under a golden laurel crown. With her golden exotically designed staff in hand, she sits upon the throne that she brought from her temple and watches the fighting silently (if any of you have seen the movie Krull, then you have a good idea of what Nike looks like <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  ) ::<br>
